Package: gbrsR
Type: Package
Title: Genome-Based Reconstruction of Strains Visualization
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2024-12-19
Author: Matthew Vincent [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Matthew Vincent <mvincent@jax.org>
Description: A comprehensive R package for visualizing genome reconstructions from GBRS (Genome-Based Reconstruction of Strains) data. Supports NPZ files containing genotypic probability matrices and generates publication-ready genome plots with configurable parameters.
